name: Galactic Entity 5
description:
Galactic Entity series is a visual representation of energy beings that visit me during Magic Mushrooms ceremonies. 
They are intelligent forms with a great sense of humour and powerful energy. They are always "dressed" in vibrant colors and they feel like a mix of humanoids + insects + jesters. They say they come from a different galaxy and use magic mushrooms as a vehicle to connect with human beings. They wish to help us raise our consciousness level.
I hope this meeting inspires and opens your mind up to a magical reality that happens beyond our five senses.
Blessings to you and yours.
